                                             java.lang.String identifier)
        Gets the TableColumnInfoDTO object for table column in the table column pool which is not deleted and has the given name. Performs a case insensitive search for table column name.
        Parameters:
        name - String the name of the table column to be searched.
        identifier - String represents the table identifier or table id.
        Returns:
        TableColumnInfoDTO table column info DTO for the table column with the given in the table column pool, returns null if no such table column is found.
